      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Wine</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Wine.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wine.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/69/Wine.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-right: 3px;\">Drink in moderation.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Information</td>\n</tr>\n\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Buff(s)</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Tipsy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Tipsy.png/24px-Tipsy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Tipsy.png/36px-Tipsy.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Tipsy.png/48px-Tipsy.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Buffs#Tipsy\" title=\"Buffs\">Tipsy</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Speed.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Speed.png/24px-Speed.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Speed.png/36px-Speed.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/94/Speed.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Speed\" title=\"Speed\">Speed</a>&#160;(−1)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Buff Duration</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 30s</span></td>\n\t</tr> \n\t<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding: 0; border: 0;\">\n\t\t\t<table style=\"width: 101%; margin-top: -2px; margin-left: -2px;\">\n\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Sell Prices</td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Base</td>\n\t\t\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\"><img alt=\"Artisan.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/46/Artisan.png/24px-Artisan.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/46/Artisan.png/36px-Artisan.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/46/Artisan.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Skills#Farming\" title=\"Skills\">Artisan</a> <i>(+40%)</i></td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><em>3 × Base <a href=\"/Fruits\" title=\"Fruits\">Fruit</a> Price</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><em>1.4 × Base Wine Price</em></td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Artisan Goods</td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Equipment</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Keg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/7c/Keg.png/24px-Keg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/7c/Keg.png/36px-Keg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/7c/Keg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a></span></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Processing Time</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 10,000m (&#8776;7d)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Ingredients</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\">Any <a href=\"/Fruits\" title=\"Fruits\">Fruit</a> (1)</td>\n\t</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<dl><dd><i> For a detailed analysis of profit using the Keg, see <a href=\"/Keg_Productivity\" title=\"Keg Productivity\">Keg Productivity</a>.</i></dd>\n<dd><i> For a full list of wine prices, see <a href=\"/Fruits\" title=\"Fruits\">Fruits</a>.</i></dd></dl>\n<p><b>Wine</b> is an <a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Good</a> made from the <a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a>, taking 7 days.  It can also be received as a gift at the <a href=\"/Feast_of_the_Winter_Star\" title=\"Feast of the Winter Star\">Feast of the Winter Star</a>.\n</p><p>The sell price of Wine depends on the <a href=\"/Fruits\" title=\"Fruits\">fruit</a> used (3 &#215; Base Fruit Value).  When consumed, wine causes a <a href=\"/Buffs\" title=\"Buffs\">Tipsy</a> buff that decreases <a href=\"/Speed\" title=\"Speed\">Speed</a> by 1. The <a href=\"/Energy\" title=\"Energy\">energy</a> and <a href=\"/Health\" title=\"Health\">health</a> restored by Wine is equal to 1.75 &#215; Base Fruit Value for edible fruit. For inedible fruit, Wine will restore energy equal to 25% Base Fruit Value and health equal to 11.25% Base Fruit Value.<sup id=\"cite_ref-wine_energy_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-wine_energy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The color of the Wine also depends on the fruit used.\n</p><p><b>Note:</b> It is possible to acquire Wine that has no base fruit (from the <a href=\"/Traveling_Cart\" title=\"Traveling Cart\">Traveling Cart</a> or a <a href=\"/Statue_Of_Endless_Fortune\" title=\"Statue Of Endless Fortune\">Statue Of Endless Fortune</a>, as a gift at the <a href=\"/Feast_of_the_Winter_Star\" title=\"Feast of the Winter Star\">Feast of the Winter Star</a>, or a New Year's Eve gift from <a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\">Leah</a> or <a href=\"/Elliott\" title=\"Elliott\">Elliott</a>). This item is simply titled \"Wine\", has a selling price of <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"400\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />400g</span> (or <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"560\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />560g</span> with the <a href=\"/Farming#Farming_Skill\" title=\"Farming\">Artisan Profession</a>), and restores 50 <a href=\"/Energy\" title=\"Energy\">energy</a> and 22 <a href=\"/Health\" title=\"Health\">health</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Aged_Values\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aged Values</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Gifting\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gifting</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Bundles\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Bundles</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Tailoring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tailoring</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quests\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quests</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aged_Values\">Aged Values</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Wine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Aged Values\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Wine can be placed inside a <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a> to age from normal quality to silver, gold, and eventually iridium quality. Iridium quality doubles the base sell price of Wine.  \n</p><p>Wine takes the longest to age of any item in <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Casks</a>. It takes 2 seasons of aging to go from basic wine to iridium quality wine.\n</p><p>Normal, silver, and gold quality Wine can be prematurely removed from a cask at any time by striking the cask with an <a href=\"/Axes\" title=\"Axes\">Axe</a>, <a href=\"/Hoes\" title=\"Hoes\">Hoe</a>, or <a href=\"/Pickaxes\" title=\"Pickaxes\">Pickaxe</a>.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Normal Quality\n</th>\n<th>Silver Quality<br />(x 1.25)\n</th>\n<th>Gold Quality<br />(x 1.5)\n</th>\n<th>Iridium Quality<br />(x 2)\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Wine.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/69/Wine.png/24px-Wine.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/69/Wine.png/36px-Wine.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/69/Wine.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>3 × <a href=\"/Fruits\" title=\"Fruits\">Fruit</a> Base Sell Price\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Wine.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/69/Wine.png/24px-Wine.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/69/Wine.png/36px-Wine.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/69/Wine.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>(3 × Base) × 1.25\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table> <i>Aged: 14 Days</i>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Wine.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/69/Wine.png/24px-Wine.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/69/Wine.png/36px-Wine.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/69/Wine.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>(3 × Base) × 1.50\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table> <i>Aged: 14 Days<br />Total: 28 Days</i>\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Wine.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/69/Wine.png/24px-Wine.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/69/Wine.png/36px-Wine.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/69/Wine.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>(3 × Base) × 2\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table> <i>Aged: 28 Days<br />Total: 56 Days</i>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gifting\">Gifting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Wine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Gifting\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Villager Reactions\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Love\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Harvey\" title=\"Harvey\"><img alt=\"Harvey Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7a/Harvey_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Harvey\" title=\"Harvey\">Harvey</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\"><img alt=\"Leah Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6e/Leah_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\">Leah</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Like\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\"><img alt=\"Abigail Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/63/Abigail_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\">Abigail