title=\"Evelyn\">Evelyn</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/George\" title=\"George\"><img alt=\"George Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/a/ad/George_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/George\" title=\"George\">George</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Gus\" title=\"Gus\"><img alt=\"Gus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Gus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Gus\" title=\"Gus\">Gus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\"><img alt=\"Haley Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Haley_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\"><img alt=\"Jodi Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Jodi_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\">Jodi</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\"><img alt=\"Kent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/8/86/Kent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\">Kent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\"><img alt=\"Krobus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/10/Krobus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\"><img alt=\"Lewis Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Lewis_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\">Lewis</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\"><img alt=\"Linus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Linus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\">Linus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\"><img alt=\"Marnie Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Marnie_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\"><img alt=\"Maru Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/23/Maru_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\">Maru</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\"><img alt=\"Pam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Pam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\"><img alt=\"Pierre Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/cf/Pierre_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\">Pierre</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\"><img alt=\"Robin Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d1/Robin_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Hate\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\"><img alt=\"Jas Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/68/Jas_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\">Jas</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\"><img alt=\"Leo Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3d/Leo_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\">Leo</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\"><img alt=\"Penny Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/bc/Penny_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Wine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Wine is used in the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Purple.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/24px-Bundle_Purple.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/36px-Bundle_Purple.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bundles#Enchanters_Bundle\" title=\"Bundles\">Enchanter's Bundle</a> on the <a href=\"/Bundles#Bulletin_Board\" title=\"Bundles\">Bulletin Board</a></span>.</li>\n<li>One silver (or better) quality wine is an option for <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Purple.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/24px-Bundle_Purple.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/36px-Bundle_Purple.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bundles#The_Missing_Bundle\" title=\"Bundles\">The Missing Bundle</a> in the abandoned <a href=\"/JojaMart\" title=\"JojaMart\">JojaMart</a></span>.</li>\n<li>Wine is one of the options for the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Orange.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png/24px-Bundle_Orange.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png/36px-Bundle_Orange.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Remixed_Bundles#Brewer.27s_Bundle\" title=\"Remixed Bundles\">Brewer's Bundle</a> in the <a href=\"/Remixed_Bundles#Pantry\" title=\"Remixed Bundles\">Pantry (Remixed)</a></span>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Wine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Wine can be used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Black Leather Jacket</a>.  <a href=\"/File:Shirt138.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt138.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Shirt138.png/24px-Shirt138.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e4/Shirt138.png 1.5x\" /></a> It can be used in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>, serving as a purple dye at the dye pots, located in <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Wine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>One Wine (of any type) may be requested by <a href=\"/Blobfish\" title=\"Blobfish\">Blobfish</a> in a <a href=\"/Fish_Pond#Quests\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond quest</a> to increase the capacity of the pond from 5 to 7.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Wine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-wine_energy-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-wine_energy_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>ObjectDataDefinition::CreateFlavoredWine</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Wine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Added ability to age in <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">casks</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Added the Missing Bundle.  Wine can now be used in Tailoring.  Can be requested in a Blobfish Fish Pond quest.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Is now an option in the Brewer's Bundle.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Wine now changes color depending on the fruit used to make it. Broke texture of basic wine.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6.2\" title=\"Version History\">1.6.2</a>: Fixed texture of basic wine. Health and Energy now scales with base fruit's values.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee\" title=\"Coffee\">Coffee</a> • <a href=\"/Green_Tea\" title=\"Green Tea\">Green Tea</a> • <a href=\"/Juice\" title=\"Juice\">Juice</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise\">Dinosaur Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Duck Mayonnaise\">Duck Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Void_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Void Mayonnaise\">Void Mayonnaise</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Oil\" title=\"Oil\">Oil</a> • <a href=\"/Truffle_Oil\" title=\"Truffle Oil\">Truffle Oil</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Aged_Roe\" title=\"Aged Roe\">Aged Roe</a> • <a href=\"/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\">Caviar</a> • <a href=\"/Jellies_and_Pickles\" title=\"Jellies and Pickles\">Jellies and Pickles</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Smoked_Fish\" title=\"Smoked Fish\">Smoked Fish</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dried_Mushrooms\" title=\"Dried Mushrooms\">Dried Mushrooms</a> • <a href=\"/Dried_Fruit\" title=\"Dried Fruit\">Dried Fruit</a> • <a href=\"/Raisins\" title=\"Raisins\">Raisins</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Misc\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Maple_Syrup\" title=\"Maple Syrup\">Maple Syrup</a> • <a href=\"/Oak_Resin\" title=\"Oak Resin\">Oak Resin</a> • <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a>  • <a href=\"/Mystic_Syrup\" title=\"Mystic Syrup\">Mystic Syrup</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414005104\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.174 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.192 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2447/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 28527/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2572/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4209/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 601 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   87.496      1 -total\n 42.47%   37.163      1 Template:Infobox\n 20.55%   17.984      4 Template:Qualityprice\n 17.03%   14.902      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 14.36%   12.561      1 Template:Description\n 12.21%   10.682      3 Template:Name\n 10.98%    9.610      4 Template:Overlayimg\n  5.96%    5.214      3 Template:Bundle\n  5.10%    4.466      2 Template:Duration\n  4.06%    3.550      6 Template:History\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2085-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414005104 and revision id 176847\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng             = Wine\n|source          = [[Artisan Goods]]\n|buff            = {{name|Tipsy|link=Buffs#Tipsy{{!}}Tipsy}}{{name|Speed|−1}}\n|buffduration    = 30s\n|sellprice       = 3 × Base [[Fruits|Fruit]] Price\n|ingredients     = Any [[Fruits|Fruit]] (1)\n|craftingstation = {{name|Keg}}\n|crafttime       = 10,000m (&#8776;7d)\n}}\n{{For|a detailed analysis of profit using the Keg|Keg Productivity}}\n{{For|a full list of wine prices|Fruits}}\n'''Wine''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made from the [[Keg]], taking 7 days.  It can also be received as a gift at the [[Feast of the Winter Star]].\n\nThe sell price of Wine depends on the [[Fruits|fruit]] used (3 &times; Base Fruit Value).  When consumed, wine causes a [[Buffs|Tipsy]] buff that decreases [[Speed]] by 1. The [[energy]] and [[health]] restored by Wine is equal to 1.75 &times; Base Fruit Value for edible fruit. For inedible fruit, Wine will restore energy equal to 25% Base Fruit Value and health equal to 11.25% Base Fruit Value.<ref name=\"wine energy\" /> The color of the Wine also depends on the fruit used.\n\n'''Note:''' It is possible to acquire Wine that has no base fruit (from the [[Traveling Cart]] or a [[Statue Of Endless Fortune]], as a gift at the [[Feast of the Winter Star]], or a New Year's Eve gift from [[Leah]] or [[Elliott]]). This item is simply titled \"Wine\", has a selling price of {{Price|400}} (or {{Price|560}} with the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Artisan Profession]]), and restores 50 [[energy]] and 22 [[health]].\n\n==Aged Values==\nWine can be placed inside a [[Cask]] to age from normal quality to silver, gold, and eventually iridium quality. Iridium quality doubles the base sell price of Wine.  \n\nWine takes the longest to age of any item in [[Cask]]s. It takes 2 seasons of aging to go from basic wine to iridium quality wine.\n\nNormal, silver, and gold quality Wine can be prematurely removed from a cask at any time by striking the cask with an [[Axes|Axe]], [[Hoes|Hoe]], or [[Pickaxes|Pickaxe]].\n\n{| class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Normal Quality\n!Silver Quality<br />(x 1.25)\n!Gold Quality<br />(x 1.5)\n!Iridium Quality<br />(x 2)\n|-\n|{{Qualityprice|Wine|3 × [[Fruits|Fruit]] Base Sell Price|quality=normal|dsv=false}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Wine|(3 × Base) × 1.25|quality=silver|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 14 Days''\n|{{Qualityprice|Wine|(3 × Base) × 1.50|quality=gold|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 14 Days<br />Total: 28 Days''\n|{{Qualityprice|Wine|(3 × Base) × 2|quality=iridium|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 28 Days<br />Total: 56 Days''\n|-\n|}\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n|hate=Sebastian,Penny,Jas,Vincent,Leo\n|love=Leah,Harvey\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\n*Wine is used in the {{Bundle|enchanter||y}}.\n*One silver (or better) quality wine is an option for {{bundle|missing||y}}.\n*Wine is one of the options for the {{bundle|brewers||y}}.\n\n==Tailoring==\nWine can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[Tailoring|Black Leather Jacket]].  [[File:Shirt138.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a purple dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\nOne Wine (of any type) may be requested by [[Blobfish]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 5 to 7.\n\n==References==\n<references>\n<ref name=\"wine energy\">See <samp>ObjectDataDefinition::CreateFlavoredWine</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.1|Added ability to age in [[cask]]s.}}\n{{History|1.4|Added the Missing Bundle.  Wine can now be used in Tailoring.  Can be requested in a Blobfish Fish Pond quest.}}\n{{History|1.5|Is now an option in the Brewer's Bundle.}}\n{{History|1.6|Wine now changes color depending on the fruit used to make it. Broke texture of basic wine.}}\n{{History|1.6.2|Fixed texture of basic wine. Health and Energy now scales with base fruit's values.}}\n\n{{NavboxArtisanGoods}}\n\n[[Category:Artisan Goods]]\n\n[[de:Wein]]\n[[es:Vino]]\n[[fr:Vin]]\n[[it:Vino]]\n[[ja:ワイン]]\n[[ko:와인]]\n[[hu:Bor]]\n[[pt:Vinho]]\n[[ru:Вино]]\n[[tr:Şarap]]\n[[zh:果酒]]"
